   <titleInfo>
      <title>Lone Cabin</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This video examines Danny Wilson's artwork "Lone Cabin", which was inspired by the experiences of Frances Fox Shambaugh during the Chimney Tops 2 Wildfires. Shambaugh, who lost her home, studio, and extensive library in the fire, also had a rental house further up the mountain. When they finally got to go up and assess the damage, Shambaugh expressed surprise. “Strange. Everything around it burned, but it was still there.”</abstract>
